data.description:
*$3195/month rent; Tenant pays for Utilities; Available Now*
*3 bed, 2 bath, 1409 SF; Pets considered on a Case by Case basis*
*First month's rent ($3195) and security deposit ($3195) due prior to move in*

Luxury 3-Bed 2-Bath Columbia City Townhome for Rent.

This luxury townhome features a well-designed floor plan, which includes 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a modern kitchen, and roof-top deck boasting scenic views. Like-new overall condition. Home has high-end finishes throughout. Unique features include mini split heat and air conditioning, an attached garage with 30v EV charging station, topside patio with patio furniture and a BBQ!

Video

Executive gourmet kitchen has ample cabinets and storage, high-end stainless-steel appliances, tile backsplash, quartz countertops, and lots of windows providing great natural light! Bedrooms are spacious with large closets containing built-in dressers, as well as having large windows and high-end paint and flooring. 

The home is close to Seward Park, Leschi, Beacon Hill, and Renton, - commute is easy whether by car, bus, walking, or light rail (two blocks away!). Steps to restaurants, coffee shops, and night life. Quick commute to most of Seattle. Local Schools close to the home include:

-Hawthorne Elementary
-Mercer Middle School
-Franklin High School

There are also numerous parks and playfields in the area as well as entertainment and plenty of top-notch restaurants! These include:
-Seward Park, Genesee Park, Lake Washington Blvd Loop, Stanley Sayres Memorial Park, Hitts Hill Park
-Jefferson Golf Center/Park, Brighton Playfield, Rainier Playfield
-Marination, Pagliacci's, Jackalope Tex-Mex and Catina, Molly Moon's, La Medusa, Geraldine's
-Ark Lodge Cinemas

This home has everything you could want and more! Email or call for a tour today!
